room_title: Escape room "Zombie Breach" by A2Z Escape in Hays
room_description:
After the zombie outbreak, you've been living in quarantine under the leadership of Carl. Until an electrical malfunction occurred today, jeopardizing the safety of everyone in the zone.
Carl is away getting much-needed supplies and your compound will be overrun with walkers unless you act fast to secure the gates and stop the breach. 60 short minutes and six switches will make the difference between life and death.
